Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.10,0:00:21.60,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ritorniamo al nostro pianeta...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.25,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Quella luce...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.75,0:00:42.10,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,È il punto di contatto col nostro mondo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.25,0:00:45.50,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma lo spostamento dimensionale è già iniziato...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.50,0:00:48.00,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Possiamo farcela in tempo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.65,0:00:52.10,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Puoi correre?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.20,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Se...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.60,0:00:59.90,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,...siamo di nuovo insieme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.00,0:01:31.90,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.40,0:01:33.90,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Uah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.50,0:01:42.20,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ellyyyyy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.30,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Krelian...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.31,0:02:09.15,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.45,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Non c'è più tempo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.80,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Questo posto sta per essere distrutto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.15,0:02:21.15,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Adesso, Dio non è più.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:25.00,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Non siete più sul loro pianeta...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.05,0:02:28.20,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,...bensì vi trovate sul vostro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.35,0:02:32.90,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Krelian... Tu non te ne andrai, è così...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.85,0:02:34.40,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:44.00,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,È da quel momento che ho smesso d'essere umano...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.40,0:02:47.45,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho commesso così tanti peccati...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.65,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,...che qualsiasi tentativo di vivere come un uomo mi è impossibile...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.30,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,L'unico che avrebbe potuto perdonarmi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.10,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,...è Dio.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.20,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Non è vero!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.80,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Sono sicuro che riuscirebbero a capirlo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.85,0:03:12.05,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,C'è ancora tanto tempo per espiare i tuoi peccati! E se c'è qualcuno che può farlo, quello sei tu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.15,0:03:17.15,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Fai sempre il pacificatore, eh, Lacan?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.15,0:03:21.60,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Forse è questo che significa essere umano...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.25,0:03:27.65,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma non cambia nulla, non posso venire...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.08,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho già preso la mia decisione.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.80,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Io camminerò con Dio.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.55,0:03:37.75,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Anche se per me non esiste più posto al quale fare ritorno...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.95,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ora devo andare...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.05,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Krelian...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.00,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,In realtà...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.30,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,...io v'invidio.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.55,0:04:11.55,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,
